  </title>
  <description type="1">
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">The main objective of the project is to contribute to the reduction of food insecurity and malnutrition of households in extreme vulnerability in the Sahel and Central-North regions of Burkina Faso. The project aims at emergency response to the needs of IDPs affected by conflict and security situation and people affected by lean saison in the same area. Chrisitan Aid will focus only on the response to IDPs needs. The project provides food and nutrition assistance.</narrative>
  </description>
